name: Weblets
body:
This is an official mirror of the java.net hosted weblets project, this project will be hosted on Git Hub until the
lock on weblets.java.net is resolved by Oracle.

Note, for now the tags could not be carried over, if you need a tagged version feel free to download it from java.net.

This is the development branch for Weblets 1.2

The current master is the development branch for Weblets 1.2
